{"tid":1122093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拍戲係咪會book左某段路 然後就可以話晒事?","createTime":"2019-04-23T17:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T19:14:32.000Z","uid":67180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1c23c9ce61d6f00d0c6ca2090299d44da8f692c8","tid":1122093,"uid":67180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T17:56:44.000Z","msg":"今日路過見到有人拍戲，對面馬路都企左堆人圍觀，一路行一路向上望下係發生緊咩事，即刻比職員喝行快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果見到啲人影相就會即刻好似風紀見到有同學偷玩電話咁衝過黎捉你再喝你唔好影<br />\n<br />\n準備roll機個陣，咁啱有車係停車場準備走，又有啲呀叔衝過去叫架車唔好出住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係你封路慢慢玩啦，到底咁樣係咩玩法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/st49QUY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fst49QUY.png&h=a412450a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7dae5754ceac8e6681d3343e37a82850bdb5649","tid":1122093,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T17:59:22.000Z","msg":"政府隻眼開隻眼閉"},{"pid":"7ec15a3976b8ff2ad74b1c46bc539f443effc015","tid":1122093,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T18:01:54.000Z","msg":"冇權 你入去吹你唔漲"},{"pid":"a50012db0fd89195a59347273b99da403714ff93","tid":1122093,"uid":43314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T18:03:18.000Z","msg":"見唔見好愛國嘅宇宙最強？"},{"pid":"70b43e708b3578e38c4767570db454af3478c714","tid":1122093,"uid":142313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b7dae5754ceac8e6681d3343e37a82850bdb5649","tid":1122093,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T17:59:22.000Z","msg":"政府隻眼開隻眼閉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T18:05:32.000Z","msg":"補充返 公眾地方拍攝無需取得拍攝許可證<br />\n除非喺政府土地產業同埋政府海域 咁就要批准<br />\n（所以公園拍攝要申請許可證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢咁寫）<br />\n<br />\n但我之前聽講可以話佢非法集會？<br />\n公眾聚集：指公眾集會、公眾遊行和在任何公眾地方舉行而與會人數在10人或以上的任何其他集會、聚集或集結"},{"pid":"dbb32e4a7375f1b10ef2238665e10ddc93803850","tid